{"tid":527882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「天使」老婆唱衰阻盧卡斯入「魔」","createTime":"2018-01-13T07:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T07:43:28.000Z","uid":333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"372176fab4045df738495fc0ae5ceb92c0e9be9f","tid":527882,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LP8yUVPm7W3rfFmF2OgoJk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=954ebb35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】盧卡斯洛迪古斯以3500萬鎊從巴黎聖日耳門加盟曼聯一事，很大機會被迪馬利亞太太破壞！<br />\n<br />\n曼聯極力爭取羅致於巴黎聖日耳門不受重用的盧卡斯洛迪古斯（Lucas Moura），有傳轉會幾近完成。不過，盧卡斯洛迪古斯的太太Larissa Saad可能是成事與否的關鍵人物。據英國《太陽報》爆料，由於PSG翼鋒迪馬利亞曾效力曼聯1季，因此Larissa向迪馬利亞太太Jorgelina Cardoso問及在英國西北部生活的事。<br />\n<br />\n由於迪馬利亞一家在「天使」效力紅魔時並不愉快，大屋更曾被企圖爆竊，因此Jorgelina向Larissa大彈當地生活，令後者對丈夫入「魔」卻步，希望跟初生女兒留在巴黎。<br />\n<br />\n今季在PSG未曾在法甲正選上陣，因此盧卡斯洛迪古斯希望加盟紅魔，以爭取上陣時間，用表現躋身巴西在今年世界盃決賽周的大軍，但現在太太有家庭考慮，未知盧卡斯洛迪古斯會以自己前途還是家人感受為重？<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"9da2d6d622df78325c6e8c544d8c471773f85c44","tid":527882,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"迪馬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9828fe56cad6473b67ef6639e390745c7ca67c","tid":527882,"uid":36049,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"真曼迷迪馬老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f7ef4c1d3397928d868e3a6b7342b19d6d7fd2","tid":527882,"uid":21061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da2d6d622df78325c6e8c544d8c471773f85c44","tid":527882,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"迪馬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3be87836820c488eeb4720a4c90f4835811460","tid":527882,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad8e627ac603cc93c394c708ec65d81e442d28f","tid":527882,"uid":21970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"迪馬終於做到件對曼有用既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc200ba88834e054052622c71dfdb882b1d0ac3","tid":527882,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:41:49.000Z","msg":"好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc88bff8a7f9c3d30677013db9f0c07e29180223","tid":527882,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"死全家啦垃圾迪馬，係你自己廢咋"}]}